and fries? ♪

19:24.115 --> 19:25.849
♪ Well, there's some
right here ♪

19:25.850 --> 19:27.584
♪ Don't you tell me no lies ♪

19:27.585 --> 19:29.419
Yeah!

19:29.420 --> 19:31.249
Burger Boy!

19:31.255 --> 19:34.357
Give 'em some straw!

19:38.529 --> 19:40.196
Oh, yeah. Aw.

19:40.197 --> 19:42.198
Yeah. Ooh!

19:42.199 --> 19:44.734
Wow! Spin!

19:44.769 --> 19:45.635
Hey, you guys want to amp

19:45.636 --> 19:47.070
things up?

19:47.071 --> 19:48.571
Plug it up!
Plug it in!

19:48.572 --> 19:50.140
What does that mean?
Plug in the amp!

19:50.141 --> 19:51.875
Oh, right! Okay.

19:51.909 --> 19:54.911
Oh, look! The kids have
a little flash mob out there!

19:54.912 --> 19:57.147
This thing's turning
into a dance party!

19:57.148 --> 19:58.581
I'm goin' out there.

19:59.617 --> 20:01.051
Dog bark solo!

20:03.487 --> 20:06.489
Lin,
I think the pit paste worked.

20:06.490 --> 20:09.426
I can't see your rash anymore.
Oh, yeah! The rash is gone!

20:09.427 --> 20:10.994
You can shave.
Yeah...

20:10.995 --> 20:12.595
What? You don't want to shave?

20:12.596 --> 20:14.264
I don't know.
I kind of like 'em now.

20:14.265 --> 20:16.266
My little Harry and Sally. Ugh.

20:16.267 --> 20:18.835
I mean, great.
Armpit hair!

20:18.836 --> 20:21.671
Cool! Madonna...

20:21.672 --> 20:23.139
Thank you!

20:23.174 --> 20:25.308
Yeah!

20:25.343 --> 20:27.510
What are you guys doing here?

20:27.511 --> 20:30.146
Isn't it almost time
for Lenny's party?

20:30.181 --> 20:33.350
Well, funny story.
Um, after you were invited

20:33.351 --> 20:36.786
to leave the band,
and you reluctantly accepted,

20:36.787 --> 20:38.421
we, um...

20:38.422 --> 20:40.223
It's not fun anymore!

20:40.257 --> 20:41.791
So you're saying you're sorry?

20:41.826 --> 20:43.493
Yeah. Want to get the band
back together

20:43.494 --> 20:45.095
and go play Lenny's party?

20:45.129 --> 20:47.263
All right.

20:47.298 --> 20:50.200
Hey! Who wants to go
to a cool sixth grader's party?

20:50.201 --> 20:52.435
Yay!
Let's lead everybody

20:52.436 --> 20:54.170
away from the restaurant!

20:54.171 --> 20:56.206
- No, no, no, no! No, no!
- Yes, yes, yes, yes!

20:56.207 --> 20:57.273
I hope Lenny's okay with this.

20:57.274 --> 20:58.942
What am I saying?

20:58.943 --> 21:00.910
He's Lenny Destefano.
You guys are gonna love him!

